=========

SPARKx509 is licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License. See LICENSE.

Third-party material
--------------------

The library source is original project code. The smoke tests use OpenSSL as an
external command-line tool to generate temporary test certificates, but OpenSSL
source code is not incorporated into this repository.

Broader X.509 validation coverage is exercised from the sibling SPARKTLS
repository using the x509-limbo test corpus under that repository's test
directory and its upstream license.
